{"tid":707113,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[又一隻新經濟股] 有才天下（6100）招股","createTime":"2018-06-18T12:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T22:04:22.000Z","uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e277ca0c53bf185a68ee3972996ade810cd359","tid":707113,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"內地招聘網站「獵聘網」母企「有才天下信息技術」（6100）將於下周二（6月19日）起至22日公開招股，計劃全球發行8,800萬股，當中一成在港公開發售。招股價介乎28.5元至35.5元，集資最多31.24億元，以每手200股計，入場費約為7,171.55元。<br />\n集資淨額的當中約40%將用於進一步提高研發能力及產品組合；25%用於擇機收購或投資與公司業務互補及支持增長策略的資產及業務；25%用於繼續改進及實施銷售及營銷計劃；10%用於營運資金及一般企業用途。預計股份於6月29日在主板掛牌，<span style=\"color: red;\">聯席保薦人為摩根士丹利及摩根大通。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪LinkedIn d frd?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 大細摩一齊出馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590669626d7a4c9e46d9d2ad96bbe9b6ceb13a1c","tid":707113,"uid":184590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"有人抽？"},{"pid":"ab60fe1f9b1fd17209684cd8efe5f5d4a457dd77","tid":707113,"uid":68728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:42:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩隻會負天下 趺到仆街喎 新經濟 靠得住既咩?"},{"pid":"e9a6015681d8db7013e4ec42dd1fb56de835e4d6","tid":707113,"uid":103035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"大細摩一齊出馬<br />\n第二日必破招股價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7167c1724cd68c11032b7d5ae1a2bc44ca51de65","tid":707113,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"連續四隻呢d新經濟股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n匯付，維信金科，有才天下，過多兩日應該仲有隻叫qeeka <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全部都諗住小米上之前最後衝剌，推晒上市<img src=\"/a